Description: Safe disk cleaner with smart suggestions and treemap
 Disk Cleaner is a Linux utility for safely reclaiming disk space.
 .
 Features:
  * Smart, process-aware cleanup suggestions (won't touch a cache your
    browser is using right now).
  * Interactive treemap and sunburst visualization of any mount.
  * Optional background watchdog with low-space notifications.
  * Destructive operations default to the user's trash folder; the
    control API blocks destructive paths — only the GUI can clean.
